	type: choice
	name: d20 dividers
	choice: d20 mode
	choice: off
	choice: all breaks
	choice: all breaks +1
	choice: all breaks +2
	choice: all breaks +3
	description: 正常地d20分隔，关闭，每一段隔断，在除第一段以外每一段隔断，等等。
